"<font class=\"text-o-color-3\">The Deluxe package is the ideal choice for "
"those who want to treat themselves with a luxurious and unforgettable photo "
"experience.<br/><br/></font>"
msgstr ""

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1958
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-3\">The Deluxe package is the ultimate option for"
" couples who want to immortalize their wedding day with the best quality and"
" service. From the early morning to the late night,<strong> I will be by "
"your side from 7am to 10pm</strong>, capturing every detail and emotion of "
"your big day. You will receive <strong>at least 450 stunning photos</strong>"
" that will showcase your beauty and happiness. The Deluxe package also "
"includes a <strong>physical album with at least 50 pages</strong> of your "
"favorite photos, and a <strong>gorgeous oiled frame of 60 x 80cm</strong> "
"that will make a great decoration for your home.</font>"
msgstr ""

